             was indicted for <rs id="t17870523-40-off207" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870523-40-off207" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870523-40-off207" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17870523-40-cd208" type="crimeDate">26th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870523-40-off207 t17870523-40-cd208"></join> last, one wooden cask, value 6 d. and 100 lb. weight of Belvidere raisins, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870523-40-victim489" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Butler
                  <interp inst="t17870523-40-victim489" type="surname" value="Butler"></interp>
